# Shared SFX Library Rules (helloknight_sfx_gui.py)

Always import SFXLibrary from helloknight_sfx_gui.py
Use the exact 24 prompts + categories (Combat, Movement, UI).
Never modify the prompts — only append the fixed consistency tag string.
Filename conversion rule: lowercase + underscores, e.g.
  "Light Attack Hit" → combat_light_attack_hit.wav
  "Wall Crumble / Secret Reveal" → movement_wall_crumble_secret_reveal.wav
Keep category names lowercase in filenames.